"><div data-mesh-id="comp-lgj9hxeainlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"><!--$--><div id="comp-lgja0n8w" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-lgja0n8w wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h1 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; text-align:center; font-size:26px;"><span style="color:#113C66;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:avenir-lt-w01_85-heavy1475544,avenir-lt-w05_85-heavy,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Notre activité</span></span></span></span></h1></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-lgj9hxec5" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-lgj9hxec5 wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span style="color:#343F64;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">SLS Formation &amp; Conseil</span></span></span><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"> est un cabinet spécialisé en formation et accompagnement RH, avec des interventions qui s’articulent sur divers services qu’elle offre à ses clients, en termes de :</span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Formation,&nbsp;<span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Consulting,&nbsp;<span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Coaching,&nbsp;</span></span></span></span>Recrutement et&nbsp;<span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Accompagnement</span></span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span class="wixGuard wixui-rich-text__text">​</span></span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Par ailleurs, les services de notre Cabinet SLS touchent aussi le volet administratif, relatif à la préparation des dossiers de formation et de demande de remboursement dans le cadre des :</span></span></p>

<ul class="font_8 color_19 wix-list-text-align wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;">
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Contrats Spéciaux de Formation (<span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">CSF</span>) en relation<span style="font-size:14px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"> </span>avec <span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">l’OFPPT</span></span></span></p>
</li>
<li class="wixui-rich-text__text">
<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Formations réalisées avec <span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">l’ANAPEC </span>(dans le cadre des <span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">FCE </span>et <span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">FQR</span>).</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-lgja2k3k" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-lgja2k3k wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><h1 class="font_2 wixui-rich-text__text" style="line-height:normal; text-align:center; font-size:26px;"><span style="color:#113C66;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-family:avenir-lt-w01_85-heavy1475544,avenir-lt-w05_85-heavy,sans-serif;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="letter-spacing:normal;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Notre mission</span></span></span></span></h1></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-lamg8bbv" class="Z_l5lU ku3DBC zQ9jDz qvSjx3 Vq6kJx comp-lamg8bbv wixui-rich-text" data-testid="richTextElement"><p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-weight:bold;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">SLS Formation &amp; Conseil</span> est un cabinet ayant pour vocation la réalisation d’un levier économique et social important pour la société et ses collaborateurs.&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p class="font_8 wixui-rich-text__text" style="font-size:16px; text-align:center;"><span class="color_19 wixui-rich-text__text"><span style="font-size:16px;" class="wixui-rich-text__text">Notre rôle ne s’arrête pas à la réalisation des formations, il s’étend au développement et au suivi de votre capital humain, afin de le rendre plus performent, plus rentable. </span></span></p></div><!--/$--></div></div></div><!--/$--><!--$--><div id="comp-lgj9hxef4" class="comp-lgj9hxef4 YzqVVZ wixui-column-strip__column"><div id="bgLayers_comp-lgj9hxef4" data-hook="bgLayers" data-motion-part="BG_LAYER comp-lgj9hxef4" class="MW5IWV"><div data-testid="colorUnderlay" class="LWbAav Kv1aVt"></div><div id="bgMedia_comp-lgj9hxef4" data-motion-part="BG_MEDIA comp-lgj9hxef4" class="VgO9Yg"><wow-image id="img_comp-lgj9hxef4" class="jhxvbR Kv1aVt dLPlxY mNGsUM bgImage" data-image-info="{&quot;containerId&quot;:&quot;comp-lgj9hxef4&quot;,&quot;alignType&quot;:&quot;center&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;,&quot;targetWidth&quot;:281,&quot;targetHeight&quot;:469,&quot;isLQIP&quot;:true,&quot;encoding&quot;:&quot;AVIF&quot;,&quot;imageData&quot;:{&quot;width&quot;:3299,&quot;height&quot;:3299,&quot;uri&quot;:&quot;59ae78be3b0a4f0fa7b3c77d21838160.jpg&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;displayMode&quot;:&quot;fill&quot;}}" data-motion-part="BG_IMG comp-lgj9hxef4" data-bg-effect-name="" data-has-ssr-src="true"><img src="/images/59ae78be3b0a4f0fa7b3c77d21838160.webp" alt="réunion d'affaires" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:50% 50%" width="281" height="469"></wow-image></div></div><div data-mesh-id="comp-lgj9hxef4inlineContent" data-testid="inline-content" class=""><div data-mesh-id="comp-lgj9hxef4inlineContent-gridContainer" data-testid="mesh-container-content"></div></div></div><!--/$--></div></section><!--/$--></div></div></section><!--/$--><!--$--><section id="comp-lc96que6" tabindex="-1" class="Oqnisf comp-lc96que6 wixui-section" data-block-l